     So I won the Supra, but wimped out and max-tuned a GTO'95MR
     anyway.  So, after starting with the 4wd, and assuming I'd use
     the Demio for FF and Lwt, I wonder if it might be better to
     start with 3dr'93si anyway.  But it needs a lot of mods before
     it can win cash without duplicate.  Trying to get all Gran Turismo
     Cups without entering any event more than once might be a real
     challenge.  Europeans, at least, can beat the TRD3000GT in Normal
     with the prize Camaro to start the cash rolling.  (But need to
     cheat to avoid an NSX field).

